425.simple_description:
Increases normal attack DMG when the Modifying Level is not lower than <color=#E78300>B</color>;
Increases Skill DMG when the Modifying Level is not lower than <color=#E78300>A</color>;
Increases Ultimate Skill DMG when the Modifying Level is not lower than <color=#E78300>S</color>;
Further increases all of the effects above when the Modifying Level is at <color=#E78300>Ω</color>.
